474
00:39:00,159 --> 00:39:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Uh, pa nisam se morao brinuti o tome u tom trenutku, ali, uh, sigurno sam se brinuo kasnije.

475
00:39:05,039 --> 00:39:06,639
