499
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Dodavala sam ono što sam znala da nedostaje dok sam to mogla shvatiti.

500
00:41:30,079 --> 00:41:30,559
[SPEAKER_01] I nemam tajnu.

501
00:41:31,119 --> 00:41:36,559
